                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The First Committee of the United Nations General Assembly met on January 18 from
                    3 to 5:50 p. m.; for the record, see United Nations document A/C.1/SR.426. Mr.
                    Austin, speaking at the opening of the session, outlined for the United Nations
                    a course of action along the lines of the passage quoted by Mr. Acheson to
                    Ambassador Franks in the memorandum of conversation, <hi rend="italic"
                        >supra;</hi> he did not, however, introduce a draft resolution.</p>
            </div>
